{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into <i>Mr Trials</i>, a single-player, physics-based platformer with charming blocky graphics that bring a playful, retro feel to every level. Navigate intricate obstacles and perform thrilling stunts in vibrant, pixel-inspired environments. Perfect for players who love the challenge of mastering unique mechanics in a visually fun and stylized world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>50 Challenging Levels:</strong> Each level is designed to test your abilities with increasing difficulty. Unlock new stages and explore diverse environments that bring fresh twists to every challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>5 Themed Worlds:</strong> Progress through themed worlds, each introducing new terrains, and environmental hazards. From desert dunes to icy peaks, each world demands a different strategy!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Golden Helmets:</strong> Outperform the regular score by hitting the highest stunt combos to earn the prestigious Golden Helmet on each level. Collect them all to show off your mastery!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Easy to Learn, Hard to Master:</strong> With intuitive controls, you'll jump, flip, and balance with ease\u2014but true mastery requires skill and precision. Only the best can complete every level with a perfect score!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to prove you\u2019ve got what it takes to conquer every level, earn all the Golden Helmets, and become the ultimate stunt master in <i>Mr Trials</i>?</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Complete Level 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3280830/5c1ff7ed587537ac3752c6ac06e33efb9921aecd.jpg"},{"name":"Complete Level 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3280830/36278d1403495e1d561e501bf915e33d15d7